#: includes/integrations/learndash/class-learndash-courses.php:520
msgid ""
"<strong>Warning:</strong> The <strong>LearnDash - WooCommerce</strong> "
"plugin is active. If access to this course is managed by that plugin, you "
"should <em>not</em> use the Link With Tag setting, as it will cause your "
